The base (no-prefix) classes are the DESKTOP design. Use `max-lg:` to override styles at tablet and below, and `max-sm:` to override at mobile only. On smaller viewports, favor single-column stacked layouts — switch multi-column desktop layouts to a stacked column with `max-lg:flex-col`.
